WEBVTT

00:02.406 --> 00:06.272
Hi, my name is Richard Schenkman, and I directed "Jerome Bixby's The Man from Earth",

00:06.398 --> 00:09.732
as well as the movie you're about to watch, "The Man from Earth: Holocene".

00:09.858 --> 00:13.803
My team and I are working very hard to make sure that every single person in the world

00:13.929 --> 00:16.834
who wants to see the movie has access to stream or download it,

00:16.960 --> 00:20.756
even to the point of uploading ourselves to the filesharing community.

00:20.882 --> 00:24.357
But while it's true that many people will have free access to the movie,

00:24.483 --> 00:26.686
that hardly means it was free to make.

00:26.812 --> 00:31.452
Dozens of people worked for months or years on the film, and they deserve to be paid,

00:31.578 --> 00:36.670
just as you deserve to be paid for the work that you do, whatever that work is, and wherever it is you do it.

00:36.796 --> 00:40.584
That's why I'm so grateful to all of you who visit manfromearth.com

00:40.710 --> 00:42.976
and make a donation, of any size,

00:43.102 --> 00:46.475
if you've watched the movie without paying for it up front.

00:46.601 --> 00:49.202
It's a global experiment in the honor system.

00:49.328 --> 00:52.781
We're asking people: "If you watch our movie, and you like it

00:52.907 --> 00:56.881
will you pay something directly to the people who made it?"

00:57.007 --> 01:01.554
Thank you again for your support, and I hope you enjoy "The Man from Earth: Holocene".

